  "original_title": "\u0db6\u0dc3\u0dca\u0db1\u0dcf\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dad\u0dca \u0daf\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dab \u0db4\u0dc5\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dd3\u0db4\u0dba\u0d9a\u0da7\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0dc3\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Rains in several western and southern provinces",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Department of Meteorology says that there will be several periods of rain today (21) in the Western Province, Galle and Matara districts.",
        "A spokesman for the department said that there will be rain or thundershowers at some places in the evening or at night in the rest of the areas, and in some places in Sabaragamuwa, Central and Uva provinces, more than 75 mm of heavy rain will occur.",
        "He said that strong winds of 40, 50 km per hour will occur in Hambantota and Matara districts from time to time.",
        "The department also states that thunderstorms may be accompanied by lightning and temporary gusty winds."
      ],
